      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Munnsville%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "Oneida Creek winds through Munnsville’s center before heading north toward Oneida Lake at the county’s edge.",
